Tried this one after dib dib and mossy. Couldn't find it and after sticking myself with gorse for the hundred time I gave up. Beidh mé ar ais...

2010-05-27T19:00:00Z : Didn't find it by annalivia
we think this cache could be gone...so we went on to grave misgivings instead!

2010-04-03T19:00:00Z : Didn't find it by niallk1234
the sun was beating down and i was hungry so i probably didnt give this cache the time it deserved. i also had failed to find "mossy". didnt no whether i was supposed to be looking in the gorse or the wall. but now after looking at the spoiler i reckon thats one of the places i checked, maybe its gone. thanks for the cache anyway.

2010-03-22T19:00:00Z : Didn't find it by Bootle
